outputs.output_descr: The focus of the Conference will be the future of Delivering as One. Based on the outcome of the Independent Evaluation of Lessons Learned from Delivering as One, the conference will focus on how DaO can be taken beyond the pilot phase, and in particular how to make it fully relevant, effective and sustainable.

project_descr: V High Level Intergovernmental Conference on Delivering as One, Tirana 27-29 June 2012.
